{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/work/basically-basic-jekyll-theme/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Basically Basic","date":"2017-03-29T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"March 29th, 2017","date_from_now":"3 years ago","last_modified_at":"2019-02-19T15:05:55.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"a year ago","path":"/work/basically-basic-jekyll-theme/","author":null,"excerpt":"Your new Jekyll default theme.","tags":["Jekyll","web development","design","open source","GitHub"],"image":null,"toc":true,"comments":false,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":true},"id":"4349f5b4-e630-511e-9f36-bfd772e0b590","html":"<p>Basically Basic is a <a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/docs/themes/\">Jekyll theme</a> meant as a substitute for the default — <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/minima\">Minima</a>. Conventions and features found there are fully supported by <strong>Basically Basic</strong>, with a few enhancements thrown in for good measure:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clean responsive design with six customizable skins</li>\n<li>Curriculum Vitæ/Resume layout powered by <a href=\"https://jsonresume.org/\">JSON Resume</a></li>\n<li>About page layout</li>\n<li>Disqus Comments and Google Analytics support</li>\n<li>SEO best practices via <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll-seo-tag/\">Jekyll SEO Tag</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-basically-basic/\" class=\"btn\">Live preview</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"browser-frame\">\n  <img data-src=\"../../images/basically-basic-theme-menu.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of page with off-canvas menu\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"browser-frame\">\n  <img data-src=\"../../images/basically-basic-theme-cv.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of CV/Resume page\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"browser-frame\">\n  <img data-src=\"../../images/basically-basic-theme-alternate-skin.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot of alternate theme skin\">\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usage\"